{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":902,"text":"When people find out\nI write about time management,"},{"time":4588,"text":"they assume two things."},{"time":7564,"text":"One is that I'm always on time,"},{"time":11747,"text":"and I'm not."},{"time":13525,"text":"I have four small children,"},{"time":14894,"text":"and I would like to blame them\nfor my occasional tardiness,"},{"time":17734,"text":"but sometimes it's just not their fault."},{"time":20365,"text":"I was once late to my own speech\non time management."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23136,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":24200,"text":"We all had to just take a moment\ntogether and savor that irony."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28972,"text":"The second thing they assume\nis that I have lots of tips and tricks"},{"time":32215,"text":"for saving bits of time here and there."},{"time":34132,"text":"Sometimes I'll hear from magazines\nthat are doing a story along these lines,"},{"time":37870,"text":"generally on how to help their readers\nfind an extra hour in the day."},{"time":41221,"text":"And the idea is that we'll shave\nbits of time off everyday activities,"},{"time":44531,"text":"add it up,"},{"time":45732,"text":"and we'll have time for the good stuff."},{"time":47930,"text":"I question the entire premise\nof this piece, but I'm always interested"},{"time":51988,"text":"in hearing what they've come\nup with before they call me."},{"time":54695,"text":"Some of my favorites:"},{"time":55871,"text":"doing errands where you only\nhave to make right-hand turns --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58801,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":59853,"text":"Being extremely judicious\nin microwave usage:"},{"time":62023,"text":"it says three to three-and-a-half\nminutes on the package,"},{"time":64770,"text":"we're totally getting in on\nthe bottom side of that."},{"time":67230,"text":"And my personal favorite,\nwhich makes sense on some level,"},{"time":69993,"text":"is to DVR your favorite shows so you can\nfast-forward through the commercials."},{"time":73769,"text":"That way, you save\neight minutes every half hour,"},{"time":76085,"text":"so in the course of two hours\nof watching TV,"},{"time":78206,"text":"you find 32 minutes to exercise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79773,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80813,"text":"Which is true."},{"time":82587,"text":"You know another way to find\n32 minutes to exercise?"},{"time":85629,"text":"Don't watch two hours of TV a day, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87985,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89025,"text":"Anyway, the idea is we'll save bits\nof time here and there, add it up,"},{"time":92523,"text":"we will finally get\nto everything we want to do."},{"time":94831,"text":"But after studying how successful\npeople spend their time"},{"time":97767,"text":"and looking at their\nschedules hour by hour,"},{"time":100428,"text":"I think this idea\nhas it completely backward."},{"time":104305,"text":"We don't build the lives\nwe want by saving time."},{"time":108566,"text":"We build the lives we want,"},{"time":110636,"text":"and then time saves itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115194,"text":"Here's what I mean."},{"time":116369,"text":"I recently did a time diary project"},{"time":118087,"text":"looking at 1,001 days in the lives\nof extremely busy women."},{"time":122315,"text":"They had demanding jobs,\nsometimes their own businesses,"},{"time":124983,"text":"kids to care for,\nmaybe parents to care for,"},{"time":127142,"text":"community commitments --"},{"time":128496,"text":"busy, busy people."},{"time":130799,"text":"I had them keep track\nof their time for a week"},{"time":133030,"text":"so I could add up how much\nthey worked and slept,"},{"time":135367,"text":"and I interviewed them\nabout their strategies, for my book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138200,"text":"One of the women whose time log I studied"},{"time":140213,"text":"goes out on a Wednesday night\nfor something."},{"time":142300,"text":"She comes home to find\nthat her water heater has broken,"},{"time":144953,"text":"and there is now water\nall over her basement."},{"time":148380,"text":"If you've ever had anything\nlike this happen to you,"},{"time":150858,"text":"you know it is a hugely damaging,\nfrightening, sopping mess."},{"time":153762,"text":"So she's dealing with the immediate\naftermath that night,"},{"time":156496,"text":"next day she's got plumbers coming in,"},{"time":158397,"text":"day after that, professional cleaning\ncrew dealing with the ruined carpet."},{"time":161921,"text":"All this is being recorded\non her time log."},{"time":164011,"text":"Winds up taking seven hours of her week."},{"time":167191,"text":"Seven hours."},{"time":169179,"text":"That's like finding\nan extra hour in the day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172834,"text":"But I'm sure if you had asked her\nat the start of the week,"},{"time":175652,"text":"\"Could you find seven hours\nto train for a triathlon?\""},{"time":179893,"text":"\"Could you find seven hours\nto mentor seven worthy people?\""},{"time":183722,"text":"I'm sure she would've said\nwhat most of us would've said,"},{"time":186437,"text":"which is, \"No -- can't you see\nhow busy I am?\""},{"time":191521,"text":"Yet when she had to find seven hours"},{"time":193342,"text":"because there is water\nall over her basement,"},{"time":196165,"text":"she found seven hours."},{"time":199055,"text":"And what this shows us\nis that time is highly elastic."},{"time":203594,"text":"We cannot make more time,"},{"time":205661,"text":"but time will stretch to accommodate\nwhat we choose to put into it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210366,"text":"And so the key to time management"},{"time":213541,"text":"is treating our priorities"},{"time":215800,"text":"as the equivalent\nof that broken water heater."},{"time":220162,"text":"To get at this,"},{"time":221336,"text":"I like to use language from one\nof the busiest people I ever interviewed."},{"time":224805,"text":"By busy, I mean she was running\na small business"},{"time":227117,"text":"with 12 people on the payroll,"},{"time":228610,"text":"she had six children in her spare time."},{"time":230657,"text":"I was getting in touch with her\nto set up an interview"},{"time":233299,"text":"on how she \"had it all\" -- that phrase."},{"time":235819,"text":"I remember it was a Thursday morning,"},{"time":237652,"text":"and she was not available\nto speak with me."},{"time":239683,"text":"Of course, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":240863,"text":"But the reason she was\nunavailable to speak with me"},{"time":243306,"text":"is that she was out for a hike,"},{"time":245270,"text":"because it was a beautiful spring morning,"},{"time":247332,"text":"and she wanted to go for a hike."},{"time":248919,"text":"So of course this makes me\neven more intrigued,"},{"time":251280,"text":"and when I finally do catch up with her,\nshe explains it like this."},{"time":254480,"text":"She says, \"Listen Laura, everything I do,"},{"time":257592,"text":"every minute I spend, is my choice.\""},{"time":261830,"text":"And rather than say,"},{"time":263005,"text":"\"I don't have time to do x, y or z,\""},{"time":265893,"text":"she'd say, \"I don't do x, y or z\nbecause it's not a priority.\""},{"time":271709,"text":"\"I don't have time,\" often means\n\"It's not a priority.\""},{"time":277075,"text":"If you think about it,\nthat's really more accurate language."},{"time":279987,"text":"I could tell you I don't have time\nto dust my blinds,"},{"time":282575,"text":"but that's not true."},{"time":283768,"text":"If you offered to pay me $100,000\nto dust my blinds,"},{"time":286232,"text":"I would get to it pretty quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287856,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":288896,"text":"Since that is not going to happen,"},{"time":290555,"text":"I can acknowledge this is not\na matter of lacking time;"},{"time":293183,"text":"it's that I don't want to do it."},{"time":294808,"text":"Using this language reminds us\nthat time is a choice."},{"time":298218,"text":"And granted,"},{"time":299415,"text":"there may be horrible consequences\nfor making different choices,"},{"time":302471,"text":"I will give you that."},{"time":303701,"text":"But we are smart people,"},{"time":305347,"text":"and certainly over the long run,"},{"time":307229,"text":"we have the power to fill our lives"},{"time":309253,"text":"with the things that deserve to be there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313204,"text":"So how do we do that?"},{"time":315127,"text":"How do we treat our priorities"},{"time":316583,"text":"as the equivalent\nof that broken water heater?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319531,"text":"Well, first we need\nto figure out what they are."},{"time":321874,"text":"I want to give you two strategies\nfor thinking about this."},{"time":324652,"text":"The first, on the professional side:"},{"time":326434,"text":"I'm sure many people\ncoming up to the end of the year"},{"time":328969,"text":"are giving or getting\nannual performance reviews."},{"time":331316,"text":"You look back over\nyour successes over the year,"},{"time":333605,"text":"your \"opportunities for growth.\""},{"time":335674,"text":"And this serves its purpose,"},{"time":338221,"text":"but I find it's more effective\nto do this looking forward."},{"time":341175,"text":"So I want you to pretend\nit's the end of next year."},{"time":344326,"text":"You're giving yourself\na performance review,"},{"time":346711,"text":"and it has been an absolutely\namazing year for you professionally."},{"time":352034,"text":"What three to five things did you do\nthat made it so amazing?"},{"time":358734,"text":"So you can write next\nyear's performance review now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362558,"text":"And you can do this\nfor your personal life, too."},{"time":364829,"text":"I'm sure many of you,\nlike me, come December,"},{"time":367482,"text":"get cards that contain these folded up\nsheets of colored paper,"},{"time":371491,"text":"on which is written what is known\nas the family holiday letter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376345,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":378007,"text":"Bit of a wretched genre\nof literature, really,"},{"time":380662,"text":"going on about how amazing\neveryone in the household is,"},{"time":383970,"text":"or even more scintillating,"},{"time":385281,"text":"how busy everyone in the household is."},{"time":387815,"text":"But these letters serve a purpose,"},{"time":389488,"text":"which is that they tell\nyour friends and family"},{"time":391719,"text":"what you did in your personal life\nthat mattered to you over the year."},{"time":395068,"text":"So this year's kind of done,"},{"time":396476,"text":"but I want you to pretend\nit's the end of next year,"},{"time":398950,"text":"and it has been an absolutely amazing year"},{"time":402172,"text":"for you and the people you care about."},{"time":405391,"text":"What three to five things did you do\nthat made it so amazing?"},{"time":410839,"text":"So you can write next\nyear's family holiday letter now."},{"time":415789,"text":"Don't send it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417006,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":418046,"text":"Please, don't send it."},{"time":421049,"text":"But you can write it."},{"time":422463,"text":"And now, between the performance\nreview and the family holiday letter,"},{"time":426201,"text":"we have a list of six to ten goals\nwe can work on in the next year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429462,"text":"And now we need to break\nthese down into doable steps."},{"time":432285,"text":"So maybe you want\nto write a family history."},{"time":434517,"text":"First, you can read\nsome other family histories,"},{"time":436794,"text":"get a sense for the style."},{"time":438080,"text":"Then maybe think about the questions\nyou want to ask your relatives,"},{"time":441311,"text":"set up appointments to interview them."},{"time":443184,"text":"Or maybe you want to run a 5K."},{"time":444669,"text":"So you need to find a race and sign up,\nfigure out a training plan,"},{"time":447854,"text":"and dig those shoes\nout of the back of the closet."},{"time":450251,"text":"And then -- this is key --"},{"time":452217,"text":"we treat our priorities as the equivalent\nof that broken water heater,"},{"time":456336,"text":"by putting them into our schedules first."},{"time":459879,"text":"We do this by thinking through our weeks\nbefore we are in them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464663,"text":"I find a really good time to do this\nis Friday afternoons."},{"time":468885,"text":"Friday afternoon is what\nan economist might call"},{"time":471457,"text":"a \"low opportunity cost\" time."},{"time":474764,"text":"Most of us are not sitting there\non Friday afternoons saying,"},{"time":477688,"text":"\"I am excited to make progress"},{"time":479591,"text":"toward my personal\nand professional priorities"},{"time":481911,"text":"right now.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":483089,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484129,"text":"But we are willing to think\nabout what those should be."},{"time":486770,"text":"So take a little bit\nof time Friday afternoon,"},{"time":488999,"text":"make yourself a three-category priority\nlist: career, relationships, self."},{"time":496382,"text":"Making a three-category list reminds us"},{"time":499604,"text":"that there should be something\nin all three categories."},{"time":503118,"text":"Career, we think about;"},{"time":504398,"text":"relationships, self --"},{"time":505929,"text":"not so much."},{"time":507272,"text":"But anyway, just a short list,"},{"time":509194,"text":"two to three items in each."},{"time":511013,"text":"Then look out over the whole\nof the next week,"},{"time":513418,"text":"and see where you can plan them in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516171,"text":"Where you plan them in is up to you."},{"time":518205,"text":"I know this is going to be more\ncomplicated for some people than others."},{"time":521691,"text":"I mean, some people's lives\nare just harder than others."},{"time":525674,"text":"It is not going to be easy\nto find time to take that poetry class"},{"time":528967,"text":"if you are caring for multiple\nchildren on your own."},{"time":532058,"text":"I get that."},{"time":533253,"text":"And I don't want to minimize\nanyone's struggle."},{"time":535484,"text":"But I do think that the numbers\nI am about to tell you are empowering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540906,"text":"There are 168 hours in a week."},{"time":545962,"text":"Twenty-four times seven is 168 hours."},{"time":551295,"text":"That is a lot of time."},{"time":554627,"text":"If you are working a full-time\njob, so 40 hours a week,"},{"time":557842,"text":"sleeping eight hours a night,\nso 56 hours a week --"},{"time":560958,"text":"that leaves 72 hours for other things."},{"time":564622,"text":"That is a lot of time."},{"time":566956,"text":"You say you're working 50 hours a week,"},{"time":568865,"text":"maybe a main job and a side hustle."},{"time":570835,"text":"Well, that leaves 62 hours\nfor other things."},{"time":573329,"text":"You say you're working 60 hours."},{"time":575253,"text":"Well, that leaves 52 hours\nfor other things."},{"time":577705,"text":"You say you're working more than 60 hours."},{"time":579771,"text":"Well, are you sure?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":581352,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583110,"text":"There was once a study comparing\npeople's estimated work weeks"},{"time":586040,"text":"with time diaries."},{"time":587459,"text":"They found that people claiming\n75-plus-hour work weeks"},{"time":590159,"text":"were off by about 25 hours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592287,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":594005,"text":"You can guess in which direction, right?"},{"time":597567,"text":"Anyway, in 168 hours a week,"},{"time":599804,"text":"I think we can find time\nfor what matters to you."},{"time":602792,"text":"If you want to spend\nmore time with your kids,"},{"time":605014,"text":"you want to study more\nfor a test you're taking,"},{"time":607343,"text":"you want to exercise for three hours\nand volunteer for two,"},{"time":610712,"text":"you can."},{"time":611890,"text":"And that's even if you're working\nway more than full-time hours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":615885,"text":"So we have plenty of time, which is great,"},{"time":617961,"text":"because guess what?"},{"time":619211,"text":"We don't even need that much\ntime to do amazing things."},{"time":622486,"text":"But when most of us have\nbits of time, what do we do?"},{"time":625708,"text":"Pull out the phone, right?"},{"time":627826,"text":"Start deleting emails."},{"time":630381,"text":"Otherwise, we're puttering\naround the house"},{"time":632492,"text":"or watching TV."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634114,"text":"But small moments can have great power."},{"time":637657,"text":"You can use your bits of time"},{"time":640094,"text":"for bits of joy."},{"time":643195,"text":"Maybe it's choosing to read\nsomething wonderful on the bus"},{"time":646088,"text":"on the way to work."},{"time":647476,"text":"I know when I had a job\nthat required two bus rides"},{"time":649899,"text":"and a subway ride every morning,"},{"time":651468,"text":"I used to go to the library\non weekends to get stuff to read."},{"time":654395,"text":"It made the whole experience\nalmost, almost, enjoyable."},{"time":659857,"text":"Breaks at work can be used\nfor meditating or praying."},{"time":663434,"text":"If family dinner is out\nbecause of your crazy work schedule,"},{"time":666652,"text":"maybe family breakfast\ncould be a good substitute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":669890,"text":"It's about looking at\nthe whole of one's time"},{"time":673044,"text":"and seeing where the good stuff can go."},{"time":676504,"text":"I truly believe this."},{"time":679054,"text":"There is time."},{"time":682981,"text":"Even if we are busy,"},{"time":685223,"text":"we have time for what matters."},{"time":687752,"text":"And when we focus on what matters,"},{"time":690312,"text":"we can build the lives we want"},{"time":692765,"text":"in the time we've got."}]},{"cues":[{"time":694638,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695817,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}